<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Eden Thim Nuoi Ah</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zailan awi ing ka hun sang muol liem chu,
 Zatam dinga kipahna chu,
 Simsen loh di'n nau bang kahna,
 Albang dah hin lawpin Lalpa angah.

[V2]
 Mung ka ie nunlui muol liem nung,
 Pek tin chungah chuong mahleh gitlohna gal lien,
 Na felna zalin kei lungngai puong ie.

[V3]
 2. Eden thim nuoiah nau bang ka kap ui,
 Na gam nuom thangvan ka tun tieng,
 Ka gitloh teu tui bang thieng ding,
 Lal Immanuel gam ninnuom achun.

[V4]
 3. Hehpihna thak zel ding lam thil ingka,
 Hun sangmuol liem ni puon bang thak,
 Thagau Thiengtho ei hihhalh in,
 Albang dah ei nemin, khuo vaksak in.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>269</hymn_number>
</song>